            },
            {
               "text": "<p><table id=\"yupana70\" class=\"tawapukllay\"><tr><th colspan=\"4\"><i>Yupana</i></th><th>Left Hand</th><th>Right Hand</th><th>Arrows</th></tr> <tr id=\"tf1\"><td id=\"tc1f1\"><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_center\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_bottom\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc2f1\"><span class=\"dot three_dot_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_up\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f1\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f1\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td><td id=\"tc5f1\"><img id=\"leftHandImg7\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('leftHandImg7', '0%')\"  /></td><td id=\"tc6f1\"><img id=\"rightHandImg7\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('rightHandImg7', '0%')\"  /></td><td id=\"tc7f1\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrows-left-right upArrowWithFA\" id=\"traineeUp7\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrows-rotate downArrowWithFA\" style=\"font-size:4em;color:#00f;\" id=\"traineeDown7\"></i></td></tr></table></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Tabela 2</b>: Movimento <i>KIMSA</i> inverso representando <i>5 − 1 = 4</i>. CSS inspirado por <htcite0>.</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "48dd9187-7ecc-4f54-a387-d9ecc2497de3",
                     "text": "W3School",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2025",
                        "month": "01",
                        "day": "27"
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "#### *PISQA* (inverso)\n\nO movimento *PISQA* inverso é usado quando temos um marcador na linha superior (valor 10) e precisamos subtrair 5. O marcador é trazido para baixo como um único marcador na casa 5 da linha atual, representando a operação",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "a62b520a-f443-4d83-ab51-b99c9a46dab8",
                     "text": "Prem, Dhavit",
                     "page": "pp. 360",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2018",
                        "month": "-1",
                        "day": "-1"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "1bb0274d-dc51-4740-ac62-4d157b06ad88",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team (2024). Yupana (Addition)",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "-1",
                        "day": "-1"
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ":"
            },
            {
               "text": "<center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF;\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF;\"><p><math mathsize=\"1.5em\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mn>10</mn><mo lspace=\"0.1667em\" rspace=\"0.1667em\">−</mo><mn>5</mn><mo lspace=\"0.1667em\" rspace=\"0.1667em\">=</mo><mn>5</mn></math></p></div></div></center>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
