            {
               "text": "<p><table id=\"yupana80\" class=\"tawapukllay\"><tr><th colspan=\"4\"><i>Yupana</i></th><th>Left Hand</th><th>Right Hand</th><th>Arrows</th></tr> <tr id=\"tf1\"><td id=\"tc1f1\"><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_center\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_bottom\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc2f1\"><span class=\"dot three_dot_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_up\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f1\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f1\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td><td id=\"tc5f1\" rowspan=\"2\"><img id=\"leftHandImg8\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('leftHandImg8', '0%')\"  /></td><td id=\"tc6f1\" rowspan=\"2\"><img id=\"rightHandImg8\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('rightHandImg8', '0%')\"  /></td><td id=\"tc7f1\" rowspan=\"2\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrows-left-right upArrowWithFA\" id=\"traineeUp8\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrows-rotate downArrowWithFA\" style=\"font-size:4em;color:#00f;\" id=\"traineeDown8\"></i></td></tr> <tr id=\"tf2\"><td id=\"tc1f2\"><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_center\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_bottom\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc2f2\"><span class=\"dot three_dot_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_up\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f2\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f2\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td></tr></table></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Tabela 3</b>: Movimento <i>PISQA</i> inverso representando <i>10 − 5 = 5</i>. CSS inspirado por <htcite0>.</p>",
               "source": [
